text: Nik Muhammad Sharif Haseefy bin Mohd Lazim (born 30 March 1997) is a Malaysian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Pahang. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian footballers Category:Pahang FA players Category:Malaysia Super League players Category:Association football midfielders
